Ranger Help for: attract
========================

SYNTAX:      attract follower
USAGE:       Primary terrain or claimed Ranger domain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     50
SKILL TYPE:  husbandry

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to attract and bond with a wild animal as a
permanent companion. The Ranger must be in their primary terrain or
within their claimed Ranger domain for this skill to work. The type of
animal attracted depends on the Ranger's primary terrain.
Once bonded, the follower will fight alongside the Ranger, can be
trained with commands, and will follow the Ranger between rooms. Each
Ranger has a limited number of followers in their lifetime - if too
many die, no more will come. Choose your battles wisely to protect
your companion.
